Prevention Checklist

General Safety:
Use strong and unique passwords for all accounts
Do not share personal information like OTP or passwords
Avoid clicking on unknown or suspicious links
Always verify messages or emails before trusting them
Keep your devices updated and secured

UPI / Payment Safety:
Never share your UPI PIN with anyone
Always check the receiver’s details before making payments
Do not accept unknown payment requests
Use only trusted apps for transactions
Enable security features like app lock or fingerprint

For emergency:
National cyber crime portal: https://www.cybercrime.gov.in
Helpline number: 1930
